African Barrick Seen a ‘Significant’ Rise in Police Presence at North Mara

-- B y   T h o m a s   B i e s h e u v e l
-- 
2011-06-01T09:07:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/african-barrick-seen-a-significant-rise-in-police-presence-at-north-mara.html
African Barrick Gold Ltd. (ABG)  Chief
Executive Officer Greg Hawkins said the police presence at the
company’s North Mara mine in  Tanzania  has seen a “significant”
increase since clashes led to intruders being shot dead last
month.  To contact the reporter on this story:
